rform-country-version-of-stand-by-your-man-at-intimate-bar-3493315">《Stand By Your Man》。</a> 。</p><p>最近，她在社交媒体上预览了一首新的乡村歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lana-del-rey-previews-new-country-song-henry-come-on-3573275">“Henry，Come On”</a> 。</p><p>除了科切拉音乐节外，今年晚些时候她还将与利亚姆·加拉格尔<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/LIAM-GALLAGHER">(Liam</a> Gallagher) 一起参加雷丁音乐节<a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-festival-2022">(Reading &amp; Leeds)</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blink-182">Blink-182 音乐节</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/primavera-sound-announce-stacked-line-up-for-2024-3545261">Primavera Sound 音乐节</a>和环<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/zach-bryan-lana-del-rey-odesza-headline-hangout-festival-2024-3568922">聊音乐节 (Hangout Festival) 等音乐节</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lana-del-rey-poses-with-gun-on-instagram-post-after-appearing-at-grammys-2024-3583835">拉娜·德雷 (Lana Del Rey) 出席 2024 年格莱美颁奖典礼后在 Instagram 上持枪合影的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
